  lines:
  - text: '"Welcome Gamer! Issa me Professor Schema, I will guide you through this
      case!"'
    mood: 1
  - text: '"Someone has tampered with our database records.We need to find out what
      query they used!"'
    mood: 4
  - text: '"Youra mission is to find all the DATA FRAGMENTS hidden in this room."
      hihi'
    mood: 0
  - text: "\"CONTROLS:\n Move \u2192 Left Joystick \nLook \u2192 Right Joystick\nInteract
      \u2192 Tap the screen\""
    mood: 3
  - text: '"Collect all fragments, solve the terminal puzzle, get the keycard and
      reach the elevator!"'
    mood: 0
  - text: '"Good luck Detective! The database is counting on you!"'
    mood: 1
